subSubSection.paragraph:
Here, all Brazilian species previously classified in
Mantispa
( Carvalho & Corseuil 1995 ; Penny 1982;
Penny & Costa 1983
) are now updated following Hoffman (2002) . The genera created by Hoffman (2002) are very consistent and all are based mainly on the male terminalia, the body parts that are of great taxonomic importance for insects.
